OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Harry
OL,4,CGarthwaite
OL,6,FHarry Garthwaite, Age 103, RAF
OL,8,FInterviewed 20 February 2024
OL,10,FDied 5 September 2024
OL,12,FA pilot who clocked up almost 2,500
OL,13,Fflying hours, Mr Garthwaite flew 23
OL,14,Fdifferent aircraft in wartime,
OL,15,Fincluding Hurricanes and Spitfires.
OL,17,FStationed near Chichester in West
OL,18,FSussex, he was told to go to RAF
OL,19,FHawkinge in Kent on the night of June
OL,20,F5.
