OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Harry
OL,4,CGarthwaite
OL,6,FHe said: "We were to pick up a lot of
OL,7,FArmy officers the following morning at
OL,8,Fseven o'clock.
OL,10,F"But we had no details about where we
OL,11,Fwere going. The Army officers were
OL,12,Fgoing to tell us that when we got
OL,13,Fthere.
OL,15,F"Not until the next morning when we
OL,16,Fwere actually in the plane did they
OL,17,Fgive away the secret.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
