OL,4,CGarthwaite
OL,6,FMr Garthwaite flew the officers to RAF
OL,7,FDown Ampney to join their units,
OL,8,Fpossibly carrying secret instructions.
OL,10,FThe military aerodrome played a key
OL,11,Frole in the airborne assault on 6
OL,12,FJune. Aircraft from there dropped
OL,13,Fmembers of the Parachute Brigade into
OL,14,FNormandy as well as towing gliders
OL,15,Fcarrying troops and supplies.
OL,17,F"The aerodrome was full of gliders and
OL,18,Ftugs,'' Mr Garthwaite added.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
